Package: SCNT
Title: Let's Make it Easier to Process the sc/sn RNA seq and st Data of Kidney
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jianbo", "Qing", email = "Dr.jianboqing@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
